### Project: socksmith — All 6 phases (Tasks #598-603)
Drop-in Python replacement for PySocks (SOCKS proxy client). Modules: _types.py (ProxyType enum: SOCKS4/4A/5/5H/HTTP), _exceptions.py (ProxyError hierarchy matching PySocks API), _socks4.py (Socks4Client with SOCKS4/4a support), _socks5.py (Socks5Client with no-auth and username/password auth per RFC 1929, IPv4/IPv6/domain address types), _http.py (HttpConnectClient with Basic auth), _socket.py (socksocket subclass of socket.socket, create_connection factory), _globals.py (thread-safe set_default_proxy/get_default_proxy), socks.py (PySocks compat shim with PROXY_TYPE_SOCKS4=1/SOCKS5=2/HTTP=3). Zero deps, Python 3.10+, BSD-3-Clause, py.typed. 64 tests pass, mypy --strict clean, CI green.

